ğŸ“Œ Why: Safe, partial cleanup â€” data loss nahi hota, sirf unwanted field hatta hai.

ğŸ—‘ï¸ 2ï¸âƒ£ deleteOne() â†’ Jab Sirf Ek Document Delete Karna Ho

ğŸ¯ Use when you want to delete a single matching record.

Example Scenario:

Admin ne ek specific user ko ban kar diya.

Ek specific order cancel karni ho.

Ek unique record (e.g. _id, email) delete karna ho.

