ğŸ“Œ Why: Batch cleanup ya data retention ke liye best.

ğŸ” 4ï¸âƒ£ findOneAndDelete() â†’ Jab Delete Karna Hai Aur Deleted Data Bhi Chahiye

ğŸ¯ Use when you want to delete and immediately get the deleted document back.

Example Scenario:

