ğŸ“Œ Why: Array cleanup ke liye best â€” poora array delete nahi hota.

âš™ï¸ 6ï¸âƒ£ $pop â†’ Jab Array Ka Pehla Ya Aakhri Element Hataana Ho

ğŸ¯ Use when array behaves like a queue or stack (FIFO/LIFO).

Example Scenario:

Recent notifications mein sirf last 10 chahiye â†’ purane automatically remove karne.

