ğŸ“Œ Why: Auto-cleanup / fixed-size list maintain karne ke liye.

ğŸ§¨ 7ï¸âƒ£ $pullAll â†’ Jab Array Se Multiple Elements Ek Saath Remove Karne Ho

ğŸ¯ Use when you know multiple specific values you want to remove from an array.

Example Scenario:

